data.description: Entire home redone inside and out- In 2020- New metal roof (limited lifetime warranty), dutch lap siding, replacement windows first floor, new windows 2nd floor, drywall, paint, all new carpeting in all 3 bedrooms and living room, ceramic tile kitchen, laminate in dining area.  Bathroom cabinets, vanity and sink all new. Kitchen cabinets and counter top all new.  Furnace, Central Air and Water Heater all new. All bathroom fixtures new. All new electric service to all outlets throughout home (no old wiring remains) with new breaker box.  All plumbing replaced throughout with pex lines. New front and back decks. Brick side walk reset. Tons of storage. Car port.  Deep yard.  Must see to appreciate.
